export const homeObjOne = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Why choose an Fivances Credit Card?',
    headline: 'Fivances offers you opportunities to earn a variety of rewards',
    description:
      'From Cash Back to AIR MILES速* reward miles. The benefits do not stop there. Many of our Credit Cards offer you Purchase Protection速 Plan1+, Fraud Protection Guarantee2, travel-related insurance benefits.',
    buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/svg-1.svg',
    alt: 'Credit Card'
  };
  
  export const homeObjTwo = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '100% SECURE',
    headline: '24/7 customer support',
    description:
      'If you want us, there is always someone to speak with you, 24/7, about whatever you need big or small. Wherever you are in the world.',
    buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/svg-5.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
  };
  
  export const homeObjThree = {
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'ELIGIBILITY',
    headline: 'Before we can consider your application, please ensure you can say yes to the following:',
    description:
      "You are a Canadian resident and have a Canadian credit file. You are of the age of majority in the province or territory of the residence",
    buttonLabel: 'Start Now',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: 'images/svg-7.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
  };
  
  export const homeObjFour = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'MANAGE YOUR ACCOUNT ONLINE',
    headline: 'With Online Services from American Express',
    description:
      'You can stay on top of your account. Check statements, set account alerts and more while you are on the go.',
    buttonLabel: 'Sign Up Now',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: 'images/svg-8.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
  };
